1.0.name: wordpress/droidpress
1.0.description: A free premium WordPress theme designed by CyberChimps.com inspired by the popular Android mobile phone operating system by Google. DroidPress features post formats support, page level SEO options, social icons, widgetized sidebar and footer, and typography support including Google Fonts.
